                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "Women needed men to care for them, with the result that men served women."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Reproductive myths forced women to remain secluded, having little contact with men."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Women had shorter life spans due to childbearing, resulting in the phenomenon of male elders."
                },
